sitate the company can then set up manufacturing in taiwan and malaysia instead when the skate manufacturer meets with a cuban representative the bluff turns into a potential deal an old shoe factory can meet all present and future needs of the skate manufacturer the factory is safe from helms burton litigation and it meets working and living conditions for employees he requires adam is against the skate manufacturer setting up operations in cuba and confronts sally if sallys deal goes through his deal to finance a bridge in america will not after adam tells her that he has also arranged financing from an american bank to the tune of 100m per year she decides to tell her client that the deal is off but then changes her mind after donald tells her that the american bank has not committed to the deal as adam claimed when the news hits the press it destroys all prospects of a deal with the american bank to avoid putting the ice skate manufacturer at further risk of takeover jack and sally propose a private placement to hockey fans 
