after a golden statue is stolen xena calls on autolycus the king of thieves to help her steal it back she and gabrielle pose as rival buyers in order to discover where the statue is being hidden 
callisto with the help of dahaks priest brings hope back into the world ares sides with dahak rather than against him he tells gabrielle that if xena kills hope the fates will cut her life thread and she will die too 
